&lt;p&gt;Hardly anyone will be surprised to learn data breaches have caused quite a lot of damage throughout 2016. New research by Risk Based Security &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://themerkle.com/2016-data-breaches-account-for-over-4-billion-stolen-records/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://themerkle.com/2016-data-breaches-account-for-over-4-billion-stolen-records/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data Breaches: An Employer&amp;rsquo;s Duty to Protect Employees&amp;rsquo; Personal&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data Breaches: An Employer&amp;rsquo;s Duty to Protect Employees&amp;rsquo; Personal Information. MSK Client Alert. January 30, 2017. Recently, there has been much &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.msk.com/newsroom-alerts-2577&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.msk.com/newsroom-alerts-2577&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

