&lt;p&gt;Among the key findings in the 110-page report is that data breaches are having a financial impact on the bottom line of victimized organizations.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.eweek.com/security/cisco-report-reveals-business-impact-of-data-security.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.eweek.com/security/cisco-report-reveals-business-impact-of-data-security.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

